OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774386358
OL,3,CGovernment to make 'plug-in' solar
OL,4,Cpanels available within months
OL,6,FNew homes will be built with solar
OL,7,Fpanels and heat pumps, while plug-in
OL,8,Fsolar panels will be available in
OL,9,Fshops "within months" for existing
OL,10,Fhomeowners, the government has
OL,11,Fannounced.
OL,13,FEnergy ministers also unveiled plans
OL,14,Ffor energy companies to offer
OL,15,Fdiscounted bills to people living in
OL,16,Fareas with wind farms on windy days
OL,17,Fwhen operators would otherwise be paid
OL,18,Fto turn off due to network constraints.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
