OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774386358
OL,3,CGovernment to make 'plug-in' solar
OL,4,Cpanels available within months
OL,6,FIt is the latest in a series of
OL,7,Fannouncements from the government
OL,8,Fdoubling down on its clean energy
OL,9,Fdrive in response to the Iran war,
OL,10,Fwhich has sent fossil fuel prices
OL,11,Fsoaring, and raising the spectre of
OL,12,Fhigh prices at the pump and rising
OL,13,Fhome energy bills later this year
OL,15,FThe announcement comes the same day as
OL,16,Fthe chancellor is due to announce
OL,17,Fprovisional further support measures
OL,18,Fthe government plans to implement
OL,19,Fshould they be needed to combat rising
OL,20,Fenergy prices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774386358
OL,3,CGovernment to make 'plug-in' solar
OL,4,Cpanels available within months
OL,6,FThe government said plug-in solar
OL,7,Fpanels, which can be easily installed
OL,8,Fwith an ordinary plug and are common
OL,9,Fin places such as Germany, where
OL,10,Fpeople hang them on balconies or
OL,11,Ffences, would soon be in the shops.
OL,13,FOfficials said they were working with
OL,14,Fretailers such as Amazon and Lidl,
OL,15,Falongside manufacturers including
OL,16,FEcoFlow, to bring them to the UK
OL,17,Fmarket, so shoppers could soon see
OL,18,Fsolar panels in the "middle of Lidl"
OL,19,Faisle and other outlets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774386358
OL,3,CGovernment to make 'plug-in' solar
OL,4,Cpanels available within months
OL,6,FThe panels cut the amount of
OL,7,Felectricity being drawn from the grid,
OL,8,Flowering bills and helping reduce the
OL,9,FUK's dependence on volatile fossil
OL,10,Ffuel markets for its electricity
OL,11,Fsupplies, the Department for Energy
OL,12,FSecurity and Net Zero (DESNZ) said.
OL,14,FThe move to speed up the delivery of
OL,15,Fplug-in solar is happening as new
OL,16,Frules come into force to implement the
OL,17,F"future homes standard", building
OL,18,Fregulations that will make solar
OL,19,Fpanels and clean heating standard in
OL,20,Fnew homes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774386358
OL,3,CGovernment to make 'plug-in' solar
OL,4,Cpanels available within months
OL,6,FUnder the new standards, homes will be
OL,7,Fbuilt with heat pumps, or linked to
OL,8,Fheating networks, rather than gas
OL,9,Fboilers, and the majority of homes,
OL,10,Fwith a few exceptions, will be built
OL,11,Fwith on-site renewable electricity
OL,12,Fgeneration.
OL,14,FThe long-awaited implementation of the
OL,15,Ffuture homes standard comes a decade
OL,16,Fafter net-zero homebuilding standards
OL,17,Fwere scrapped.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774386358
OL,3,CGovernment to make 'plug-in' solar
OL,4,Cpanels available within months
OL,6,FOfficials said the measures on new
OL,7,Fhomes could save up to #830 a year on
OL,8,Feach property's energy bills, compared
OL,9,Fto a standard home with an energy
OL,10,Fperformance certificate (EPC) rating
OL,11,Fof C, and create at least 75% less
OL,12,Fcarbon emissions than those built to
OL,13,Fthe 2013 standards.
OL,15,FPointing to the conflict in Iran,
OL,16,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband said it
OL,17,Fhad, "once again shown our drive for
OL,18,Fclean power is essential for our
OL,19,Fenergy security so we can escape the
OL,20,Fgrip of fossil fuel markets we don't
OL,21,Fcontrol.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774386358
OL,3,CGovernment to make 'plug-in' solar
OL,4,Cpanels available within months
OL,6,F"Whether through solar panels fitted
OL,7,Fas standard on new homes or making it
OL,8,Fpossible for people to purchase plug-
OL,9,Fin solar in shops, we are determined
OL,10,Fto roll out clean power so we can give
OL,11,Four country energy sovereignty."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
