OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774386358
OL,3,CGovernment to make 'plug-in' solar
OL,4,Cpanels available within months
OL,6,FThe moves have been welcomed by the
OL,7,Fenergy sector, with Dhara Vyas,
OL,8,Findustry body Energy UK's chief
OL,9,Fexecutive, describing the future homes
OL,10,Fstandard as a "landmark moment" for
OL,11,Fclean energy in Britain.
OL,13,F"New homes built under this standard
OL,14,Fwill benefit from clean heating
OL,15,Fsolutions and solar, protecting
OL,16,Fhouseholds from volatile gas prices
OL,17,Fand putting energy security within the
OL,18,Fhome itself.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774386358
OL,3,CGovernment to make 'plug-in' solar
OL,4,Cpanels available within months
OL,6,F"Combined with higher fabric
OL,7,Fefficiency standards, these homes will
OL,8,Fbe warmer and cheaper to run `
OL,9,Foffering real and tangible change in
OL,10,Fpeople's homes."
OL,12,FShe added that the new standards would
OL,13,Fgive businesses the long-term
OL,14,Fcertainty they needed to invest in
OL,15,Fmanufacturing, scale up supply chains,
OL,16,Fand build a skilled workforce.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
